Things were getting a little cramped, there would surely be a leak 
somewhere in thier little group. " Ah good day my friend, My name is 
Phobia (They haven't met yet right?) just having a little 
hypothetical discussion,." He knew that if word got to Megatron then 
he'd be served up on a spit, unless he could find another scapegoat. 
He was filled with information and his ship was full of technology. 
If a compitent Predacon leader got hold of this information they'd be 
victorious. In Megatrons hands all life as they knew it would have 
never existed.
